details: All the glitz of glam rock (without the spandex or bad hair). Urban Decay's Heavy Metal Glitter Eye Liner is a water-based, buildable liner that contains super-fine glitter in a clear base that dries down quickly and REALLY stays put. The glitter is suspended in a gel, so it won't separate in the bottle (which means you don't need to shake the bottle like you do with watery formulas). Peach and cucumber extract condition the skin, while carrot extract smooths and softens. The precise, thin-tipped brush makes it easy to create fine, glittery lines. Want more sparkle? Use the side of the brush to sweep sparkle all over your lids. Or, for an even bolder, jewel-encrusted look, remove the wiper (the little piece that controls how much product comes out of the bottle) and tap on Heavy Metal with your fingers.Urban Decay is 100% cruelty-free.Lock in any look for up to 16 hours with Urban Decay All Nighter Makeup Setting Spray.
